Zomato Restaurant Data Analysis using Excel, SQL, Python, and Power BI
# Zomato Data Analysis Project

## Project Overview
This project analyzes Zomato restaurant data to identify trends in ratings, restaurant categories, online ordering behavior, and customer popularity.

## Tools Used
- Excel for data cleaning
- MySQL for SQL analysis
- Python for exploratory data analysis
- Power BI for interactive dashboard visualization

## Key Insights
- Dining restaurants dominate the platform
- Restaurants with online ordering tend to have slightly higher ratings
- Most restaurants fall between 3.5 and 4.2 rating

## Dashboard
Power BI dashboard shows:
- Rating distribution
- Restaurant type distribution
- Online order vs rating
- Most popular restaurants by votes

